query:
insert into feeds (
                id,
                source_title,
                feed_url,
                site_url,
                last_synced_at,
                last_sync_result,
                sync_started_at
            ) values ($1, $2, $3, $4, now(), 'success', NULL)
            on conflict (feed_url) do update set
                source_title = $2,
                site_url = $4,
                updated_at = now(),
                sync_started_at = NULL,
                last_synced_at = now(),
                last_sync_result = 'success'
            returning id
